OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,FResident doctors in Scotland have
OL,7,Fvoted in favour of strike action for
OL,8,Fthe first time over pay, as their
OL,9,Fcounterparts in England stage a five-
OL,10,Fday walkout.
OL,12,FBritish Medical Association (BMA)
OL,13,FScotland confirmed the strike will run
OL,14,Ffrom 7am on 13 January to 7am on 17
OL,15,FJanuary 2026.
OL,17,FThe union said the Scottish Government
OL,18,Fcannot "brazenly renege" on its
OL,19,Fcommitments without being "held to
OL,20,Faccount," but added it still hopes for
OL,21,Fa negotiated resolution.
