OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,FScottish Health Secretary Neil Gray
OL,7,Fsaid he was disappointed by the result
OL,8,Fand had offered to meet the BMA
OL,9,FScotland chairman on Monday.
OL,11,FA five-week ballot with resident
OL,12,Fdoctors revealed that almost 92% of
OL,13,Fthose who voted were in favour of
OL,14,Fstrike action.
OL,16,FWith 5,185 resident doctors in
OL,17,FScotland eligible to vote, turnout was
OL,18,F58% with a total of 3,008 votes cast.
