OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,FDr Chris Smith, chairman of the BMA's
OL,7,FScottish resident doctors committee,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The result of this ballot shows
OL,9,Fthat resident doctors in Scotland are
OL,10,Funited in anger over the Scottish
OL,11,FGovernment breaking the deal they
OL,12,Fagreed over pay just two years ago.
OL,14,F"This is not where we wanted to be.
OL,15,FHowever, we have sent a message loud
OL,16,Fand clear - the Government cannot
OL,17,Fbrazenly renege on its commitments
OL,18,Fwithout expecting to be held to
OL,19,Faccount.
