OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,F"Instead of negotiating with resident
OL,7,Fdoctors to make credible progress
OL,8,Ftowards pay restoration, as they
OL,9,Fagreed to do, they have imposed a pay
OL,10,Fuplift that is the lowest average
OL,11,Faward received by resident doctors
OL,12,Fanywhere in the UK.
OL,14,FStrikes by resident doctors in England
OL,15,Fhave forced the cancellation of
OL,16,Fthousands of operations and procedures.
OL,18,FAn ongoing five-day walkout, ending at
OL,19,F7am on Monday 22 December, is adding
OL,20,Fto the disruption.
