OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer called the
OL,7,Faction "dangerous and utterly
OL,8,Firresponsible."
OL,10,FThe strikes come amid a record flu
OL,11,Fseason, with NHS leaders warning of a
OL,12,F"huge strain on hospitals" and further
OL,13,Fdelays to care.
OL,15,FGray said: "I am disappointed that BMA
OL,16,Fresident doctors have voted to take
OL,17,Fstrike action and I have offered to
OL,18,Fmeet the chair of the BMA residents
OL,19,Fcommittee on Monday December 22.
