OL,3,CResident doctors in Scotland vote to
OL,4,Cstrike for first time over pay
OL,6,F"Our top priority for our patients and
OL,7,Fthe workforce is to improve waiting
OL,8,Ftimes, access to the NHS and positive
OL,9,Foutcomes. Industrial action will put
OL,10,Fall that progress at risk."
OL,12,FResident doctors, previously called
OL,13,Fjunior doctors, make up almost half of
OL,14,Fthe medical workforce in Scotland. A
OL,15,Fresident doctor can be newly qualified
OL,16,For have up to 10 years' experience.
